org.apache.edgent.runtime.jobregistry

Class JobRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.edgent.runtime.jobregistry.JobRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JobRegistryService

    public class JobRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
implements JobRegistryService
    Maintains a set of registered jobs and a set of listeners. Notifies listeners on job additions, deletions and updates.

      • addListener

        public void addListener(BiConsumer<JobRegistryService.EventType,Job> listener)
        Description copied from interface: JobRegistryService
        Adds a handler to a collection of listeners that will be notified on job registration and state changes. Listeners will be notified in the order in which they are added.

        A listener is notified of all existing jobs when it is first added.

        Specified by:
        addListener in interface JobRegistryService
        Parameters:
        listener - the listener that will be added
